data.title: Karaoke Catalog
data.meta_description: 10863702.pdf - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document provides a list of over 400 songs that are available in the karaoke catalog, organized into categories like "Top 50", musicals, decades, and genres. It includes popular artists and songs from various decades ranging from the 1930s to current times. The catalog can be accessed online at a specified website for virtual karaoke singing.
